### Register User
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@email.com",
  "password": "123456"
}